### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}
@accessToken = 
@invoiceId = 

GET {{apiUrl}}/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get versions of an invoice (requires merchant auth)

### Example response
// 200 OK
// {
//   "status": "success",
//   "message": "Invoice versions retrieved successfully",
//   "data": [ { /* version objects */ } ]
// }
